{"tid":147691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾南山:內地H7N9增 病毒現變異","createTime":"2017-03-08T04:56:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T05:09:20.000Z","uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"839e4ce8b2ffe85e52aabd25dabf2d47c99ca566","tid":147691,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T04:56:37.000Z","msg":"中國工程院院士、廣州呼吸疾病國家重點實驗室主任鍾南山表示，內地今年至今共錄得367人感染H7N9禽流感個案，按年有所增加，其中116人死亡，死亡率約30%。<br />\n<br />\n鍾南山稱，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>染病個案增加的其中一個原因，是病毒出現變異。其中兩例變異的H7N9病毒株，在人類身上發現，表明已變異病毒可傳染給人</strong></span>，雖然現在未出現人傳人的個案，但不能排這可能性，不能掉以輕心，呼籲市民不要買活雞回家。<br />\n<br />\n他又表示，病毒會否在人體身上引起更嚴重的病徵，及增加人傳人的危險性，仍未有充分證據證明。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1507728/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F1507728%2F&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=df42df9b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1507728/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鄰國又送厚禮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e3e50d688955acffc71faae85d2d2737a8dcc05","tid":147691,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T05:02:33.000Z","msg":"支爆未？"},{"pid":"246c1b486e02572536931d02957340620ad45a97","tid":147691,"uid":35914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T05:09:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支爆未？</blockquote><br />\n死咁d人咪可以拎佢地d錢吊多陣介先"}]}